Please change room 312's suite to another standard room.

146
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:17,150
Were you the guest who stayed in room 312 before?

147
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:17,960
Yes.

148
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:19,510
Here's the thing.

149
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:21,310
The lakeside dinner

150
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,290
