158
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,200
Hello.

159
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,640
Are you Mr. Zhou Yu from room 312?

160
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,270
Here's the thing.

161
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,350
A lady

162
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:16,670
