for you in the kitchen.

167
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:46,670
In my hometown,

168
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,300
we eat this on our birthdays.

169
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:53,420
You'll be one year older

170
00:09:53,450 --> 00:09:57,110
after eating these boiled glutinous rice balls in fermented glutinous rice.

171
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:58,710
But today is not my birthday.

172
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,960
Did you even remember my birthday wrongly?

173
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:03,950
No.

174
00:10:03,950 --> 00:10:05,350
I saw this date

175
00:10:05,350 --> 00:10:06,680
in your grandpa's room.

176
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,280
It's not your birthday?

177
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,070
No.

178
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:11,630
Fine.

179
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,660
