184
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:32,670
No.

185
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:34,690
Catch a cold?

186
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,960
If I catch a cold,

187
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:41,480
Yu will come to see me.

188
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:44,290
I'm not going home.

189
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:45,750
I'm not going home.

190
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,350
I'm not going home.

191
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,110
I think this is wrong.

192
00:10:50,310 --> 00:10:53,040
You shouldn't be like this when you love someone.

193
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,410
Love

194
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,490
will make you a better person,

195
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,540
instead of making you lose...

196
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,320
So beautiful.

197
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:13,790
Why is Zhou Yu so romantic?

198
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:23,900
I spent a lot of money on this

199
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:26,570
for Yu.

200
00:11:33,990 --> 00:11:34,620
What's wrong?

201
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,750
Did you catch a cold?

202
00:11:36,010 --> 00:11:36,610
I'm fine.

203
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:38,620
It's because the wind's blowing.

204
00:11:39,610 --> 00:11:40,820
It's really pretty.

205
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:27,100
I've dealt with the situation with the classmates.

206
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:28,560
They're leaving tonight.

207
00:12:29,570 --> 00:12:31,240
Thank you for today, Tingjiang.

208
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:33,240
I hope you can keep the secret for me.

209
00:12:36,090 --> 00:12:37,230
I won't ask

210
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,800
