214
00:12:43,190 --> 00:12:44,720
Call me if you need help.

215
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:46,430
OK.

216
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,600
Hello.

217
00:13:05,990 --> 00:13:07,190
